      "description": "Affably Evil: She's the more moderate end of Red Flag and her words are rarely cruel or tempermental. Dating Catwoman: Her and Gary's friendship has strong echoes of this. Foil/Evil Counterpart: For Gary. Freudian Excuse: She got involved with Red Flag because she was tired of being written off as stupid and wanted to prove what she was capable of. Killed Off for Real:In the DOD raid during \"Original Sin\".Not Quite Dead:AFreeze-Frame Bonusduring a commercial shows graffiti that says \"@Anna_Lives.\" This is aTwitteraccountseemingly owned by Anna, who responds to questions in-character. Turns out that it's just Gary, though, as a misguided way of honoring her memory.",
